{"tid":1870203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我啱啱先知我屋企口罩過晒期","createTime":"2020-02-08T16:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T16:12:22.000Z","uid":281692,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4df966f552f098e3922989439a7b1ac2890d9ab5","tid":1870203,"uid":281692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"啱啱我阿爸傾電話，我聽到我屋企啲口罩係10幾年前，2005年已經到咗期...<br />\n<br />\n我已經戴過幾個，又發現有幾個仲要係殘次品，一個無鐵線，一個污糟咗，仲有一個獨立包裝無封實...<br />\n<br />\n我聽日先買到新口罩，即係我聽日仲要戴過咗期10幾年嘅口罩出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#林鄭呢個廢柴媽媽<br />\n#光復香港 時代抗疫<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#我的史詩家庭"},{"pid":"d9b8761485f5d532925efa2c8a6083f255b2cafd","tid":1870203,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"可以用"},{"pid":"11c88ad1093d253eeb212d658dc81abf6fc8eec0","tid":1870203,"uid":139294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"我都係呀 不過冇爛 照用緊"},{"pid":"6495cf30676341bc22852cd1778f3e172e802eeb","tid":1870203,"uid":281692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"Made in China<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}